fields.title: Business Analyst
fields.description: Analyze business processes, gather requirements, develop and implement data-driven solutions, and collaborate with stakeholders to improve operations.
fields.requirements: Bachelor's degree in Business Administration or related field, 2+ years of experience in business analysis, strong skills in Excel and SQL.

fields.title: Software Engineer
fields.description: Design, develop, and maintain software applications, work on cutting-edge technology projects, and collaborate with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality solutions.
fields.requirements: Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or related field, 3+ years of experience in software development, proficiency in Python and Java.

fields.title: Software Engineer
fields.description: Develop and maintain software applications, collaborate with cross-functional teams, and ensure high performance and responsiveness of applications.
fields.requirements: Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or related field, 3+ years of experience in software development, proficiency in C# and .NET framework.

fields.title: Data Scientist
fields.description: Analyze large datasets to extract meaningful insights, develop predictive models, and support data-driven decision-making processes.
fields.requirements: Master's degree in Data Science or related field, 2+ years of experience in data analysis, strong skills in Python and SQL.

fields.title: Product Manager
fields.description: Lead product development from concept to launch, define product vision and strategy, and work closely with engineering, design, and marketing teams.
fields.requirements: MBA or equivalent experience, 5+ years of experience in product management, excellent communication and leadership skills.

fields.title: UX Designer
fields.description: Create user-centered designs, conduct user research and usability testing, and collaborate with product and engineering teams to enhance user experience.
fields.requirements: Bachelor's degree in Design or related field, 2+ years of experience in UX design, strong portfolio showcasing design skills.

fields.title: Mechanical Engineer
fields.description: Design and develop mechanical systems and components, conduct testing and validation, and collaborate with manufacturing teams to ensure product quality.
fields.requirements: Bachelor's degree in Mechanical Engineering, 3+ years of experience in mechanical design, proficiency in CAD software.
